-- Namibia Breweries 6-Month After-Tax Profit Rose 7%
-- B y   C h a m w e   K a i r a
-- 2012-03-15T13:20:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/namibia-breweries-6-month-after-tax-profit-rose-7-correct-.html
Namibia Breweries Ltd. (NBS)  said after-
tax profit for the 6 months through December rose 7 percent to
120 Namibian dollars.  Earnings per share gained 9 percent as revenue advanced 13
percent, the Windhoek-based brewer said in an e-mailed statement
today. The company declared a dividend of 27 cents per share.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chamwe Kaira in  Windhoek  at 
 ckaira@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
